以下是一些常用的指令，所有的指令均可用 help <指令名称> 获得较详细的说明。
 
[一般指令]
go, inventory, skills, drop, emote, give, ask, close, get
look, open, brief, score, party, search, put, lock, secure
 
[沟通用指令]                  [查询状态用指令]
describe, emote, converse     faq, finger, levels, bug, idea
say, tell, reply, shout       news, time, praise, typo, query
ignore, wizcall, temote       who, version, uptime, upsince
 
[战斗用指令]          [使用者介面指令]       [有关系统的指令]
wimpy, wear, kill     do, alias, history     okip, set, passwd
hp, wield, remove     nickname, inactive     chfn, suicide
consider, tactic                             hibernate, save
 
[其它指令]
依职业会有一些附加指令，请查寻各公会。
